ing: 4 pounds bone-in chicken breast halves with skin
1 (8 ounce) can pineapple chunks with juice
n: Take The Night Off Slow Cooker Pineapple Chicken
des: "Served with brown rice and steamed broccoli, it makes a nice Asian-style meal. It's a nice, mild dish."
ins: Place chicken breasts into the bottom of a slow cooker. Pour pineapple chunks with juice over chicken. Drizzle with honey and soy sauce and sprinkle with brown sugar and ginger. Set cooker on High and cook for 1 hour. Reduce setting to Low and cook until chicken is cooked through, moist, and tender, about 6 more hours.
